  "title": "Mechanical Engineer",
  "description": "<p>In this role, you will have the unique opportunity to engage in Mechanical Design, using Solidworks and AutoCad.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We're looking for motivated engineers willing to work in a quality driven environment with a keen sense of product development to produce technologically superior products. One thing is for sure, you will be working closely with an experienced team, that will always make you feel that you a part of a dynamic organization.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Responsibilities</p>\n<p>• Mechanical Design</p>\n<p>• New project development, involving in conceptual design proposal, design and compilation of project budget.</p>\n<p>• Responsible for meeting product quality standards and delivery target.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<p>• Degree/Diploma in Mechanical/Mechatronics/Precision Engineering</p>\n<p>• Interest in Industrial Automation field</p>\n<p>• Knowledge of Solidworks/Pro E or other 3D CAD software</p>\n<p>• Preferably at least 2 years of relevant experience in Industrial Automation projects</p>",
